=======
rstblog
=======

My NIH static blog replacement for my old dynamic blog.

Totally nothing new but does the trick for me.

Install
=======

Using virtual environments
--------------------------

Writing commands for getting a virtual environment up & running::

	virtualenv venv
	venv/bin/easy_install pip
	venv/bin/pip install pyyaml
	venv/bin/pip install babel
	venv/bin/pip install blinker
	venv/bin/pip install jinja2
	venv/bin/pip install docutils
	venv/bin/pip install werkzeug

Then create the blog using the virtual environment::

	venv/bin/python run-rstblog.py
